      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Born of necessity to contend with violent storms on the world of Shimrinsara in the Vast, </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">harness lightning </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">enables you to collect energy from major electrical discharges that occur within the area of the spell. The spell&rsquo;s area grants cover against ranged attacks and area effects that would deal only electricity damage. The bonus to saving throws due to this cover applies to any save against a critical hit effect from a weapon that deals only electricity damage. The first time the spell&rsquo;s area grants cover against an attack or effect this way, collected electrical attacks bend toward you and form a surging sphere of pure energy that lasts until the end of the spell. You can take a standard action to discharge this sphere at a target within 100 feet, dealing 8d8 electricity damage.</span></p>"
